00:44:53.142 --> 00:44:56.862
You can see that they're functionally far more polyfunctional.

797
00:44:56.942 --> 00:45:00.102
They secrete more cytokines per cell, TNF, gamma interferon.

798
00:45:00.402 --> 00:45:04.282
But one of the biggest signatures we see is their ability to synthesize

799
00:45:04.382 --> 00:45:07.891
IL-2, both in the lymph node and in the tumor microenvironments.

800
00:45:07.972 --> 00:45:09.522
And we know this is really critical.

801
00:45:09.532 --> 00:45:12.992
It's the first thing to go in exhaustion is IL-2 production, but we still see that

802
00:45:13.002 --> 00:45:16.482
happening here. The T cells are also

803
00:45:16.502 --> 00:45:20.082
therapeutically superior. This is without any lymphodepletion or anything else like

804
00:45:20.122 --> 00:45:22.522
that, just a bulk transfer of 10 million T cells.

