00:45:36.202 --> 00:45:39.742
blockade. Okay. So to conclude this part of the talk,

810
00:45:40.022 --> 00:45:43.922
actually the talk in general, TCR stimulation talks directly

811
00:45:43.962 --> 00:45:47.622
to the mitochondrial machinery. So especially chronic stimulation remodels the

812
00:45:47.642 --> 00:45:51.472
mitochondria away from being importers to becoming exporters.

813
00:45:52.062 --> 00:45:55.882
One of these transporters, and we're targeting all members of the SLC25 family to

814
00:45:55.902 --> 00:45:59.102
explore this, but one is the citrate carrier encoded by

815
00:45:59.242 --> 00:46:03.142
25A1, and it's upregulated by both TCR stimulation and

816
00:46:03.202 --> 00:46:07.182
metabolic stress. And that cytosolic citrate is converted to

817
00:46:07.192 --> 00:46:10.862
acetyl-CoA, where it can form lipid droplets as well as hyperacetylate

818
00:46:10.922 --> 00:46:14.442
proteins. The acetylation affects key proteins involved in T cell

